data.description: 4 bedroom + 2 bathroom corner lot home on a cul-de-sac with a pool in a quiet and desirable neighborhood. Living room has a fireplace and dual sliding doors that open up to the backyard. Great opportunity to make it your own. Easy commute to Ventura or Santa Barbara, 10 mins from downtown Ojai.
